// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1944 — Mass File Rename (icefire)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 728f782f-0464-5b10-af11-e54df0db9b68

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
